7.2.1 sphere_func

f <- sphere_func
res <- run(X0, f, dist = dist, step = step)
[1] "Laplace train time: 59.965409"
[1] "IMSE train time: 32.474940"
[1] "rmse1: 0.000276"
[1] "rmse2: 0.000560"
plot3d(x1, x2, res$z, zlab = "real function")
plot3d(x1, x2, res$pm1, zlab = "Laplace")
plot3d(x1, x2, res$pm2, zlab = "IMSPE")
